{"tid":1471823,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［打氣Post] 一句講晒 818你出唔唔出嚟","createTime":"2019-08-14T11:23:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T12:05:06.000Z","uid":49312,"like":45,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"1a3573d38262ea99c5c82ab32adbbc9df560d73b","tid":1471823,"uid":49312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T11:23:44.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我淨係為大家打氣</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">818大遊行，將會係呢場運動，割不割蓆嘅分水嶺</span></span></strong></strong><br />\n<br />\n不割蓆，唔係唔檢討<br />\n不割蓆，唔係唔指點<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">但檢討過後，你依然會係我身邊，我依然會係你身邊，互相依賴不分你我，知道大家係一個命運共同體，先至稱得上真不割蓆</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">如果一切發生後，下個行動就見唔到你了，你事實上就係割咗蓆</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n所以廢話唔講，我淨係想同大家打氣，造吓勢<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">818，民陣大遊行，你出定唔出？</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n正皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 梗係出佢老母，少人姐係運動趨向完結，好快分化<br />\n負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不了，頂唔順，太暴力，我唔再支持了"},{"pid":"ac7c5261f747e7b876c75d513eca0a2120fe9a99","tid":1471823,"uid":49312,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T11:24:24.000Z","msg":"希望大家以行動表現出核彈都唔割嘅精神"},{"pid":"f209cd0a89fcb45b87cf74df63eecbe807ba70fb","tid":1471823,"uid":49312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T11:24:37.000Z","msg":"希望大家以行動表現出核彈都唔割嘅精神"},{"pid":"74fc9114fe910090e2ef8fbe8478cc4a853cfceb","tid":1471823,"uid":49312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T11:24:49.000Z","msg":"希望大家以行動表現出核彈都唔割嘅精神"},{"pid":"004bb08b335e2e0211fdf8e7f95475ba0578e8ce","tid":1471823,"uid":49312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"